latestPosts.caption: Last few days spent at workshop with @adishaktitheatre was the most enriching experience I have had as an Actor so far. Also at many levels even as a human. Even as a soul. I realised the humongous intensity of my love for Art. When life throws you down, your only job is to get up and save your soul. Because life for sure will keep throwing you down. But is there any other better option than nourishing your soul with its true calling? Is there any other better option than saving the purity of your innocence with art? After all Artist is the Child Who Survived. 🤍 Thank you @nimmyraphel and @vkvinayadishakti for all your teachings 🙏
